 policies at institutional and sector level. ','oai:sro.sussex.ac.uk:134'),(10945,'publisher',15,'HEFCE','oai:sro.sussex.ac.uk:134'),(10946,'date',15,'2005-05','oai:sro.sussex.ac.uk:134'),(10947,'type',15,'Reports and working papers','oai:sro.sussex.ac.uk:134'),(10948,'type',15,'NonPeerReviewed','oai:sro.sussex.ac.uk:134'),(10949,'format',15,'application/pdf','oai:sro.sussex.ac.uk:134'),(10950,'identifier',15,'http://sro.sussex.ac.uk/134/1/negotiating_equity.pdf','oai:sro.sussex.ac.uk:134'),(10951,'identifier',15,'Deem, R., Morley, L and Tlili, A (2005) Negotiating Equity in UK Universities. Project Report. HEFCE, London, UK.','oai:sro.sussex.ac.uk:134'),(10952,'relation',15,'http://www.hefce.ac.uk/pubs/rdreports/2005/rd10_05/','oai:sro.sussex.ac.uk:134'),(10953,'relation',15,'http://sro.sussex.ac.uk/134/','oai:sro.sussex.ac.uk:134'),(10954,'title',15,'Comedy of Manners: Quality and Power in Higher Education','oai:sro.sussex.ac.uk:173'),(10955,'creator',15,'Morley, L.','oai:sro.sussex.ac.uk:173'),(10956,'subject',15,'LB2300 Higher education','oai:sro.sussex.ac.uk:173'),(10957,'publisher',15,'SRHE/Open University Press','oai:sro.sussex.ac.uk:173'),(10958,'contributor',15,'Trowler, P.','oai:sro.sussex.ac.uk:173'),(10959,'date',15,'2002','oai:sro.sussex.ac.uk:173'),(10960,'type',15,'Book Chapter or Section','oai:sro.sussex.ac.uk:173'),(10961,'type',15,'PeerReviewed','oai:sro.sussex.ac.uk:173'),(10962,'identifier',15,'Morley, L. (2002) Comedy of Manners: Quality and Power in Higher Education. In: Trowler, P. (ed.) Higher Educational Policy and Institutional Change: Intentions and Outcomes in Turbulent Environments. SRHE and Open University Press imprint . SRHE/Open University Press, Buckinghamshire, UK, pp. 126-141. ISBN 9780335209194','oai:sro.sussex.ac.uk:173'),(10963,'relation',15,'http://sro.sussex.ac.uk/173/','oai:sro.sussex.ac.uk:173'),(10964,'title',15,'Reconstructing Students as Consumers: Power and Assimilation?','oai:sro.sussex.ac.uk:180'),(10965,'creator',15,