 used in other ways.\r\n\r\nThese resources have been developed by: National Oceanography Centre, Southampton project led by Toby Tyrrell and Andrew Yool, focus on how the Earth system works. ','oai:edshare.soton.ac.uk:103'),(21938,'date',12,'2008-04-02','oai:edshare.soton.ac.uk:103'),(21939,'type',12,'Resource','oai:edshare.soton.ac.uk:103'),(21940,'type',12,'NonPeerReviewed','oai:edshare.soton.ac.uk:103'),(21941,'format',12,'text/html','oai:edshare.soton.ac.uk:103'),(21942,'format',12,'application/vnd.edshare-link','oai:edshare.soton.ac.uk:103'),(21943,'identifier',12,'http://www.edshare.soton.ac.uk/103/1/index.php','oai:edshare.soton.ac.uk:103'),(21944,'identifier',12,'http://www.noc.soton.ac.uk/jmodels/index.php','oai:edshare.soton.ac.uk:103'),(21945,'identifier',12,'Jmodels: Java models of earth system regulation - UNSPECIFIED\n Keywords:Oceanography, Biogeochemistry, Earth systems modelling, Computer systems modelling \n','oai:edshare.soton.ac.uk:103'),(21946,'relation',12,'http://www.edshare.soton.ac.uk/103/','oai:edshare.soton.ac.uk:103'),(21947,'title',12,'EdShare: Sharing for learning and teaching','oai:edshare.soton.ac.uk:111'),(21948,'date',12,'2008-04-02','oai:edshare.soton.ac.uk:111'),(21949,'type',12,'Resource','oai:edshare.soton.ac.uk:111'),(21950,'type',12,'NonPeerReviewed','oai:edshare.soton.ac.uk:111'),(21951,'format',12,'application/vnd.ms-powerpoint','oai:edshare.soton.ac.uk:111'),(21952,'identifier',12,'http://www.edshare.soton.ac.uk/111/1/EdShare_Learning_and%20_teaching_week_2008.ppt','oai:edshare.soton.ac.uk:111'),(21953,'identifier',12,'EdShare: Sharing for learning and teaching - UNSPECIFIED\n Keywords:edshare, learning and teaching repositories, Learning and teaching \n','oai:edshare.soton.ac.uk:111'),(21954,'relation',12,'http://www.edshare.soton.ac.uk/111/','oai:edshare.soton.ac.uk:111'),(21955,'title',12,'Human heart','oai:edshare.soton.ac.uk:113'),(21956,'description',12,'This is some text providing a basic anatomical introduction to 